move chocolate ganache logs from fridge and trim either end through cling film, using a sharp knife dipped in hot water. Cut 3 even cylinders from each log then remove cling film.","Place a ganache cylinder on a plate. Place some grated walnuts next to it then add a scoop of ginger ice cream on top of walnuts. Dot pear purée around the plate. Arrange pear discs and remaining grated walnuts over the plate. Dress with a little coriander cress before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Chocolate and Sesame Ganache","content":["125 g double cream","½ tsp cocoa powder","50 g liquid glucose","¾ tsp fine sea salt","200 g dark chocolate (64%), small pieces or callets","200 g milk chocolate, small pieces or callets","3 egg yolks, from medium eggs","50 g sesame oil","25 g vegetable oil","250 g double cream, semi whipped (soft peak stage)"]},{"title":"Ginger Ice Cream","content":["750 g whole milk","250 g double cream","75 g liquid glucose","40 g trimoline","30 g milk powder","50 g fresh root ginger, grated","200 g egg yolks","100 g caster sugar","20 g stem ginger in syrup, syrup only","50 g stem ginger, chopped in small pieces"]},{"title":"Pear Purée","content":["3 pears, medium, peeled, cored (approx. 300 g)","30 g unsalted butter","50 g caster sugar","½ lemon, juice only"]},{"title":"Garnish","content":["16 halved walnuts, for grating over plates","4 pears, medium, peeled, sliced (1 mm) then cut in 2 cm discs","coriander cress, for garnish"]}],"id":"r178688","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-wu0zgo4khIk\/XZWc2pBW09I\/AAAAAAAAefo\/s3KDwZ6b_08wFcxTijI6EHsFi43S__NPgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_7_YUJifeNVt49Fv_.png","title":"Chocolate and Sesame Ganache","publishedAt":"2017-10-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"60 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"54 g","calories":"3347 kJ \/ 806 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, fine mesh sieve, long sharp knife, jug, ice cream machine, fridge, freezer","hintsAndTricks":["Slice the pears on a mandolin into <nobr>1 mm